{"id":161273,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011614/","date":"2011-06-15T05:30:35Z","modified":"2011-06-15T05:30:35Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/6/14","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【热点时评】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约客》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.newyorker.com/online/blogs/evanosnos/2011/06/truth-rumors-and-fruit-baskets.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国来信：真相、谣言和果篮</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“当愤怒与技术相结合后，一个小贩的命运也能改变历史”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国见红</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://seeingredinchina.com/2011/06/14/re-thinking-chinese-stability/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对中国稳定的再思考</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“中国政府已经把很多人灌输到了分不清批评政府与人身攻击的程度”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110614/ap_on_re_as/as_china_unrest\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国南方骚乱发生地戒备森严</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“居民被要求晚上不要外出，也不要在网上发布照片”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业内幕》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/the-bigger-debt-problem-chinas-local-government-debt-vs-us-subprime-debt-2011-6?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+businessinsider+%28Business+Insider%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的地方政府债务比美国的次贷危机更严重</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“美国的次贷不超过</span><span>GDP10%</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，中国的地方债务超过</span><span>GDP30%</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"OLE_LINK4\"></a><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"OLE_LINK3\"><span></span></a><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/15/business/15yuan.html?_r=1&#038;partner=rss&#038;emc=rss\"><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国大力抑制通货膨胀</span></span></span><span><span></span></span></a></span><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“中国政府对于由食品和汽油价格飙升带来的生活费用上升和社会紧张加剧十分敏感”</span></span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/environment/blog/2011/jun/14/three-gorges-dam-quality-award\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">尽管存在迫切问题，三峡大坝仍获得最高质量奖</span></a> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——是因为它造成了“高质量”的污染和滑坡吗？</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“如是说”分析</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.alsosprachanalyst.com/economy/china-economy-risk-of-hard-landing-increases.html?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+AlsoSprachAnalyst+%28Also+sprach+Analyst+%28Main%29%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国经济硬着陆风险在增加</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——最新一组通胀、固定资产和消费数据表明硬着陆可能性上升</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">卡内基国际和平基金会</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.carnegieendowment.org/publications/index.cfm?fa=view&#038;id=44596&#038;utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+carnegie%2Fchina+%28DC+-+Region+-+China%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国增长不平衡的迷思</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“即使中国存在持续的贸易顺差，也不能说中国的增长就是不平衡的”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《时代》周刊</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,2077139,00.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的最新出口产品：股票欺诈</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“在中国公司中，类似东南融通这样的现象并不少见”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国法律博客</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinalawblog.com/2011/06/yahoo_alibaba_alipay_jack_ma_and_what_really_happened_and_what_it_means.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">关于雅虎</span>/<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">阿里巴巴的八个问题</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“中国政府很可能正在幕后调解，争取合理地解决此事”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亚洲哨兵：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.asiasentinel.com/index.php?option=com_content&#038;task=view&#038;id=3252&#038;Itemid=367\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国在南海问题上的“险恶”立场</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“中国眼里的南海不仅是西沙和南沙群岛，而是整个水域”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外交政策研究所</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.fpri.org/enotes/201106.pant.china_india.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国与印度：正在形成中的分庭抗礼</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“中印任何一方的行动都被另一方理解为对自己的威胁”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《基督教科学箴言报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.csmonitor.com/World/Asia-Pacific/2011/0614/China-pushes-rail-links-into-southeast-Asia-Is-Laos-aboard?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+feeds%2Fworld+%28Christian+Science+Monitor+%7C+World%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国把铁路修进东南亚，老挝人对此不太情愿</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——老挝村民也面临到了拆迁问题</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华盛顿邮报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia-pacific/australian-prime-minister-snubs-dalai-lama-but-says-her-decision-was-not-influenced-by-china/2011/06/14/AG8XlBUH_story.html?wprss=rss_asia-pacific\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">澳大利亚总理冷落达赖喇嘛，称并非受中国的影响</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“他在过去四年里来了五次，不是每次都见总理”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110614/pl_nm/us_china_usa_huntsman\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">特别报道：洪博培从中国起步走向白宫</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“总的来说，他给中国政府留下了正面的印象”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110614/pl_nm/us_china_usa_military_counterfeit\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国参议院要求中国协助调查山寨武器零件案</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“中国拒绝给调查人员发放入境签证”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《华盛顿时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2011/jun/7/our-chief-rival-in-intelligence-wars/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">书评：我们主要的情报战对手</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——《老虎陷阱：美中之间的秘密谍战》</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【社会百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">上海点滴</span><span> &#8211; <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://shanghaiscrap.com/?p=6595#more-6595\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">非自然选择：重男轻女</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“性别不平衡是经济发展当中的副产品”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国辩论：</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.chinadebate.com/2011/06/new-south-china-mall-worlds-largest-and-empty/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">新南华商城</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——世界最大也是最空荡荡的商城</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">迷途老外</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.lostlaowai.com/blog/expat-stuff/teaching-esl-in-china/an-open-letter-to-chinese-students-going-abroad/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">给中国留学生的公开信</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“说点故乡故国的负面消息没有什么大不了的。”</span><span></span></p>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-6208183498318799489?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":278,"categories":[1],"tags":[]}